# Try build, deploy, and expose a php application via S2I

1) Deploy a new app based on a simple php repository (i.e. https://github.com/jtdagmaj/PHP_helloworld)

2) Check if a BuildConfig was fired by the DeploymentConfig and follow its output

3) After the build, check if a Pod was correctly scheduled and a Service was created

4) Expose the Service and retrieve the exposed url

5) Try accessing it with a browser

